ay":2225826,"title":"Wycliffe's Bible","description":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Joane de Valence was born in Canterbury, Kent, England as the daughter of Sir Stephen de Valence of Repton and Joan de Saye. She married Sir Thomas Fogge in 1416, in Kent, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. She died on 8 July 1420, in her hometown, and was buried in Canterbury, Kent, England."},"et":{"–8 July 1420":"–8. juuli 1420","1350–1420":"1350–1420","–1420":"–1420","–1407":"–1407","1390–Male":"1390–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1330–1397":"1330–1397","1325–1378":"1325–1378","about 1390":"umbes 1390","Aft 1359":"pärast 1359","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1390":"1390","13 July 1407":"13. juuli 1407","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1325":"1325","1378":"1378","29 June 1378":"29. juuni 1378","1453":"1453","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","after 1397":"pärast 1397","8 July 1420":"8. juuli 1420","1407":"1407","1416":"1416","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Ripton, Kent, England":"Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Repton, Derbyshire, England":"Repton, Derbyshire, England","England":"England","Herstmonceux, Sussex, England":"Herstmonceux, Sussex, England","Sawbridgeworth, Hertsfordshire, England":"Sawbridgeworth, Hertfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, England"},"fi":{"–8 July 1420":"–8. heinäkuuta 1420","1350–1420":"1350–1420","–1420":"–1420","–1407":"–1407","1390–Male":"1390–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1330–1397":"1330–1397","1325–1378":"1325–1378","about 1390":"noin 1390","Aft 1359":"1359 jälkeen","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1390":"1390","13 July 1407":"13